{"tid":948324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊受成：女大不中留","createTime":"2018-12-20T03:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T04:29:04.000Z","uid":48905,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"191dede8c8e62608478ba33d6ce25d069f9e47e5","tid":948324,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"英皇集團主席楊受成出席電影《神探大戰》煞科宴，提到最近旗下藝人鍾欣潼（阿嬌）、周勵淇先後結婚，他笑言：「好，最好嫁晒，佢哋年紀都應該，搵到啱就結，女大不中留，不過我唔會催佢哋，有啱就結囉！（要準備大禮？）我冇所謂，大家合作咗十幾年，佢哋對公司好有貢獻，我對個個都一視同仁。（淨番蔡卓妍同容祖兒未結婚？）仲有好多，我都希望佢哋早日搵到個好歸宿。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGReH13.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGReH13.gif&h=a0996322&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08120ddcf7bec12078a2846af34352fb3eacfa69","tid":948324,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"希哥相簿.rar"},{"pid":"b240652633e5e6f41873c234f71dfa0719619e12","tid":948324,"uid":8636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"女大不中出？"},{"pid":"1ebf50bda68fc8aad6cd8444abb591792f0bc90c","tid":948324,"uid":78016,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"呀sa 唔係未結婚喎<br />\n唔好考我記性<br />\n佢好似係失婚喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ecdbb336bb0bc810e597eb694e962eaaf8866b","tid":948324,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"佢地無清算陳冠希算唔算係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c97a796896874160753ef8682dddd31bac92589","tid":948324,"uid":119494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"成哥好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba99a8c888de73bf9ed880aa71aeff052073283","tid":948324,"uid":119210,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"變尻態 成世要做你隻雞咩<br />\n你當自己老幾 你估你係皇